Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.60,Default (Small),,0,0,0,,I took my baby on a Saturday bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我带着宝贝在周末开车兜风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.40,Default (Small),,0,0,0,,Boy, is that girl with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.00,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,人问「小伙子, 这是你的姑娘吗?」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.40,Default (Small),,0,0,0,,Yes, we're one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我答「是的, 我们心心相印, 合二为一」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.80,Default (Small),,0,0,0,,Now I believe in miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我相信奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.80,Default (Small),,0,0,0,,and a miracle has happened tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而今夜奇迹已经显现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.80,Default (Small),,0,0,0,,But, if, you're thinkin' about my baby,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你在意我的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:02.00,Default (Small),,0,0,0,,it don't matter if you're black or white.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你是黑是白  我都不在意
